&lt;p&gt;My family presented new headphones to me.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;WH-CH700N | SONY
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’m sensitive to sounds from childhood.
It’s difficult for me to distinguish human’s voice at a busy place.
On the other hand, sometimes I’m get distracted by the slightest sound in a quiet room.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My friend gave me advice to get a tool for protecting my ears.
That’s why I got headphones. It’s so nice.
